title: THURSDAY - Drew Brees return? 2020
itunes:title: THURSDAY - Drew Brees return? 2020
description:
Taysom Hill and the Saints taking on Jalen Hurts and the Eagles on Sunday, but when will Drew Brees return? (:0:25) Dak Prescott (1:29) out for the year, but Stephen Jones gives an update on his contract talks (1:49)...Steelers run game could be getting a boost (3:01), we have the latest on James Conner, as well as an update on Christian McCaffrey's (3:14) latest injury, plus some good news for Seattle's backfield (3:56)
